high_descs: Turn right and step forward around the counter and turn left to face it.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Cut the potato on the counter into slices.
Look up to face the counter.
Place the knife on the counter.
Look up to face the potato on the counter.
Pick up a slice of potato on the counter.
Turn around and step forward to face the fridge.
Cool the potato slice in the fridge and remove it.
Turn around and cross the room, then turn right and cross the room and turn right to face the trash can.
Place the potato slice in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: To cool a potato slice plus place it in the trash can.

high_descs: Turn around, go forward a bit, turn left, go forward, turn left to the counter
Pick up the knife on the counter
Slice the potato on the counter
Move a bit to the right
Put the knife on the counter
Move a bit to the left
Pick up a potato slice from the counter
Turn left, go forward, turn left and go to the fridge
Put the potato slice in the fridge, wait, pick up the potato slice from the fridge
Turn around, go forward, turn right, go forward, turn right and go to the bin
Put the potato slice in the bin
anns.task_desc: Cool a slice of potato and put it in the bin

high_descs: move right to the table
pick up the knife
slice the potato on the table
move right on the table
drop the knife there
move left to the potato
pick up a slice
move left to the fridge
cool the slice in the fridge and take it out
turn around and move to the bin
trash the slice in the bin
